Components Required for Prototype

Arduino Uno – 2 units

XBee Wireless Modules – 2 units

Traffic Light LED Sets – 4 units

Timing LEDs – 3 per light (Total: 12 units)

Sound Sensors – 4 units

Ultrasonic Sensors – 8 units

Boom Barriers – 4 units

Servo Motors – 4 units (one for each barrier)

HC-05 / Bluetooth Module – 1 unit

Breadboards & Jumper Wires – assorted

5V Power Supply / USB Cable
